reviews.review_text:
built to last I just realized the other day how much I love the lyrics to this song.   Such a mature composition for Hunter/Garcia.

The song itself showcases some great Garcia singing and an awesome MIDI solo - a trademark of 1990.

GREAT great recording, thanks to all that made this happen!!

ted, ted, ted ted mattes'(s?) tapes are WONDERFUL, bless ya

we already know these spring '90 shows are out of this world but i have to say these are some of my favorite sounding auds ever. i only wish he'd gotten some of the other dates (3/15&16 are FAVS) but just a one of these would be enough to be eternally grateful for... and look at us, we got a sweet little bunch. bless ya, ted, and those of you who got these gems to our ears
